<br>
Another amusing bit, if anyone has played the other two realms, they might note that there is a lack of snakes in Hibernia.  In RL Irish lore, St. Patrick got rid of all the snakes by some sort of miracle. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#110d03><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/unaoltan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Naoltan </A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hibernian Defender Trainee</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#006400>(3/18/02 8:07:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub49.ezboard.com/fhiberniaonguiniverefrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lack of actual Roleplaying on our server</span><hr size=1> KellieghM,<br>
