<br>
Good: Greetin's friends!  What mischief and merriment have ye planned for the evenin'?<br>
Bad: yo, sup<br>
<br>
Good: I must say, this situation's more than a little confusing.<br>
Bad: wtf?<br>
<br>
Good: Har!  Ye surely were cut down a notch by Angabhalagabh's witty retort!  Ye'd be well served to learn the virtues of silence and humility.<br>
Bad: lol, pwnd!<br>
<br>
Good: Good Master, could a poor fool like myself possibly trouble you for some small assistance with the day's hunt?<br>
Bad: can u buff me plz?<br>
<br>
Good: Ah yes, I do believe I understand your advice.  I shall take it to heart and do my best to follow your wisdom.  My humble thanks for your assistance, mistress.<br>
Bad: kthx<br>
<br>
Good: inc!<br>
Bad: I have gained the foe's attention and I'm en route to the group so we may dispatch him and make off with his loo....ah crap he killed me while I was typing.... rez plz.<br>
